heading: IGW408I SMSVSAM SUCCESSFULLY TERMINATED AT END OF MEMORY
content:
Explanation

  The SMSVSAM server has successfully ended.

  System action

  The system continues processing.

  Operator response

  None

  System programmer response

  If the SMSVSAM server does not automatically restart and it needs to
  be active, use the VARY SMS command to restart it.

  Problem determination

  None

  Source

  DFSMSdfp

  Module

  IDAVSEOX
